name: Nightmare 1 - The old Man
description: "Is it future or is it past?" That's what the old man asked himself. I didn't understand him, not at first. When I looked into his eyes I could see the flames and emptiness, a kind of nowhere, a temperature below 0 emanating from his heart. This was neither a man nor a demon, it was much less than that, and much more too. ( This is the first piece of my spooky sound collection, inspired in Twin Peaks! Also is my participation in #FEAR4HEN)
